channel.title: SlewScape 742 IS BACK!
channel.description:
[center] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2qimmb9.png[/img][/center]
718/742 Runescape Private Server
Have you been looking for something different? The new hype? Tired of all these servers who have unfinished features, not enough features, or are just down right rude?
Then welcome to SlewScape! As the owner of SlewScape, my goal is to make the server into what the players want. I don't just take suggestions and throw them out, I take them, write them down, spread the word; and if popular demand says so, I add the suggestion!
So what can we possibly add that is different from any regular server? To be honest, no matter how much we code, plan, etc, in the end every private server is the same when it comes to features. But thats just features.. At SlewScape we strive to have the perfect staff, members who are there for you, listen to what you say, and help you in any possible way!
Don't be one of the silly ones who log in and think this server is just like any other one, don't be a fool! Stick around and you are sure to see the servers true colors!
So what are you waiting for? Go play!
Download webclient: [size=14pt](It may take some time to load at start and when you login, so give it some time download the cache :D)[/size] If you are still lagging in game open your graphics settings>custom>and choose opengl or any other display mode which suits you! [url=https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/51734385/SlewScape.jar]https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/51734385/SlewScape.jar[/url]
[b]Webclient:[/b] [url=http://www.slewscape.info/webclient.html]http://www.slewscape.info/webclient.html[/url]
forums : [url=http://www.slewscape.info]www.slewscape.info[/url]
Features: [b]Quests[/b] [b]Custom bosses[/b] [b]Vote4items[/b] Eco based. Perfect PvM/PvP/Prayers. Perfect switching. All skills are working! Regular Donator and Extreme donator zone! Fully working barbarian agility course + advanced! Fully working Gnome agility course + advanced! Godwars dungeon reworked! (you now require killcounts for bosses!)
A huge list of Player versus Monster teleports. Many working aura's, like Supreme corruption, Salvation and Harmony. All for sale! Squeal of fortune. Xp Counter. Money Pouch. No items lost on death, unless you die in the wilderness, or in any unsafe PvP zone or at Corp! Nex sets with HP bonusses. Awesome xp in skilling, and combat. Including automated double EXP weekends. Easy teleporting/traveling. Handy noticeboard, which allows you to change your display name, and character look. Custom shop names, so it will be easy to find what you need. Loyality system: this gives you 250 points for playing each 30 minutes, these points can be used to buy aura's at the loyality shop. Nice starters!
Home is easily accesed by typing ::home. If you need some cash fast, try thieving a bit. you could also loot anything you find, everything can be sold. If you need any help, feel free to add khayam to friends ingame and just ask, also any other online member of staffs too!
have a nice time!
